            <title><![CDATA[【#主食摄入不足会引起疲劳# [思考]】#吃主食为什么能让人快乐# 医生提醒，膳食的基础是主食，正常人如果没有主食供能，一方面大脑运作的效率会大大下降，另一方...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%BB%E9%A3%9F%E6%91%84%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E4%BC%9A%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E7%96%B2%E5%8A%B3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%BB%E9%A3%9F%E6%91%84%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E4%BC%9A%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E7%96%B2%E5%8A%B3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#主食摄入不足会引起疲劳#</span></a> <span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%90%83%E4%B8%BB%E9%A3%9F%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%A9%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%AB%E4%B9%90%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%90%83%E4%B8%BB%E9%A3%9F%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%A9%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%AB%E4%B9%90%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#吃主食为什么能让人快乐#</span></a> 医生提醒，膳食的基础是主食，正常人如果没有主食供能，一方面大脑运作的效率会大大下降，另一方面，人体也会开始燃烧肌肉供能，造成肌肉丧失，时间长了之后，人会变得乏力、没劲儿。血糖异常的人，比如糖尿病患者，如果不摄入主食，身体会燃烧大量脂肪产热，从而产生大量的酮体，有可能会导致严重的酮症酸中毒。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B8%B8%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%83%E7%A2%B3%E6%B0%B4%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E6%A0%B7%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B8%B8%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%83%E7%A2%B3%E6%B0%B4%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E6%A0%B7%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#常年不吃碳水的人怎么样了#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6NlC21z" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
